{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"616","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"微軟砸重金 消除碳排放","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-01-17 23:12 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報 編譯林奇賢／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>微軟加入對抗氣候變遷的行列，承諾消除過去所有的碳足跡，並將投資<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>億美元開發減碳技術，以履行更遠大的氣候承諾。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>華爾街日報報導，微軟<span lang='EN-US'>16</span>日宣布將在<span lang='EN-US'>2030</span>年前實現「負碳排放」（<span lang='EN-US'>carbon negative</span>）－也就是從大氣中吸收的二氧化碳量，甚至比本身營運和整個供應鏈製造排放量還多。相較矽谷一些主要競爭對手許下的承諾，微軟無疑跨出更大一步。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>微軟表示，將在<span lang='EN-US'>2050</span>年前，消除自<span lang='EN-US'>1975</span>年成立以來該公司製造的所有碳排放。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>微軟說，將在未來四年為自家的氣候創新基金（<span lang='EN-US'>Climate Innovation Fund</span>）提供設立<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>億美元，以開發除碳技術。在目前計劃減碳的大企業中，微軟的氣候宣言最有雄心壯志。微軟表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2012</span>年來一直致力「碳中和」（<span lang='EN-US'>Carbon Neutral</span>），透過購買碳補償（<span lang='EN-US'>Carbon Offset</span>）抵銷相應的排放量，並且資助森林保育等可吸收二氧化碳的計畫。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>微軟計劃<span lang='EN-US'>2025</span>年前所有用電皆來自可再生能源，微軟園區內的車輛也將在<span lang='EN-US'>2030</span>年前全部改用電動車。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>麥肯錫永續實踐部門全球主管皮納表示，愈來愈多投資人、消費者和企業員工都希望企業界做出改變。過去數年來，美妝業者萊雅（<span lang='EN-US'>L&#39;Or</span>&eacute;<span lang='EN-US'>al</span>）、製藥業者諾和諾德（<span lang='EN-US'>Novo Nordisk</span>）、食品業者瑪氏食品（<span lang='EN-US'>Mars</span>）等公司都投入減碳的計畫。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4294709</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-22","clk_count":"133"}},"__N_SSG":true}